What you need to know:  Absa Kip Keino Classic meeting director Barnaba Korir has announced the gate charges for the World Athletics Continental Gold Tour event due for May 7 at KasaraniKorir disclosed that participants for men and women’s 10,000m and 400m hurdles alongside men’s 400m will be picked from the national championships that end FridayThere will be nine core events on card during the Kip Keino Classic; men and women’s hammer throw, women’s long jump, men and women’s 3,000m steeplechase, men and women’s 200m, men’s 100m and men’s pole vault